title: XEXYZ - Primeval Mountain (ReIssue 2008)  mp3    2014
description:
XEXYZ - Primeval Mountain (ReIssue 2008)  mp3    2014 What we got...XYZ
"Primeval Mountain"

First recording from this one-man NES Black Metal project of J.R. Preston (Tjolgtjar, Blood Cult, Enbilulugugal). He uses borrowed samples from old Nintendo games and mixes them with lo-fi Black Metal. Originally issued in 2006 by Dipsomaniac Records, this is the 2008 re-issue by Suffering Jesus/xSangueRecordSx, with a different track order than the original and a bonus track.
